Package: prssim
Title: Estimate Prevalence Of Elevated PRS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Michael", "Levin", , "michael.levin@pennmedicine.upenn.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9937-9932"))
Description: A set of functions designed to estimate the prevalence of
    elevated polygenic risk among relatives of probands, and estimate the
    prevalence of disease among relatives of probands with elevated
    polygenic risk. The functions are obtained from:
    https://doi.org/10.1101/2021.04.11.439.
